| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0891 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 43f0ed13-34b7-58c2-a35e-36123bcd7a23"
